casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Arthur Jay SMITH.
No. D-3044.
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 5, 2019.
Arthur Jay Smith, of Pittsburg, Pennsylvania, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
